      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "At issue is a feature of bankruptcy law known as a non-debtor release, which the Sackler family — owners of opioid maker Purdue Pharma — is trying to use to ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "children": [
              {
                "detail": 0,
                "format": 0,
                "mode": "normal",
                "style": "",
                "text": "shield its entire corporate empire",
